# 🎨 One-Shot UI/UX Design Prompt — Foodinesia CCTV-SOP Dashboard

> **Tujuan:** Prompt ini bisa diberikan ke AI design tool (v0, Cursor, Claude, dll) untuk menghasilkan desain UI/UX lengkap seluruh halaman dan fitur dashboard CCTV-SOP monitoring system.

---

## 📋 PROMPT

```
Desain UI/UX lengkap untuk "Foodinesia CCTV-SOP Dashboard" — sebuah web application dashboard untuk monitoring kepatuhan SOP (Standard Operating Procedure) di area produksi pabrik menggunakan sistem CCTV + AI (YOLOv8 object detection & face recognition).

════════════════════════════════════════════
KONTEKS PROYEK
════════════════════════════════════════════

Aplikasi ini digunakan oleh supervisor dan manajemen pabrik untuk:
1. Memantau CCTV secara real-time dengan AI yang otomatis mendeteksi pelanggaran SOP (helm tidak dipakai, baju tidak dimasukkan, dll)
2. Melihat riwayat insiden dan foto bukti pelanggaran
3. Mengelola identitas staff (untuk face recognition)
4. Mengatur konfigurasi sistem AI detection

Tech Stack: React + Vite + TailwindCSS (frontend), Flask + Socket.IO (backend)
Target User: Supervisor pabrik, manajemen, admin IT
Device: Desktop-first (1920x1080), responsive ke tablet (1024px)
Theme: Dark mode utama (slate-900 background), mewah, profesional, industrial-modern

════════════════════════════════════════════
DESIGN SYSTEM & TOKENS
════════════════════════════════════════════

COLOR PALETTE (wajib dipakai konsisten):
- Background utama: #0f172a (slate-900)
- Surface / Card: #1e293b (slate-800)
- Border: #334155 (slate-700)
- Text primary: #e2e8f0 (slate-200)
- Text secondary: #94a3b8 (slate-400)
- Text muted: #64748b (slate-500)
- Accent sky (primary): #38bdf8
- Success / emerald: #10b981
- Warning / amber: #f59e0b
- Danger / rose: #f43f5e
- Info / cyan: #06b6d4
- Violet (accent sekunder): #8b5cf6

TYPOGRAPHY:
- Font family: "Inter" atau "Segoe UI"
- Heading: Bold, tracking tight
- Body: Regular, 14-16px

SPACING: 4px base unit, 8/12/16/24/32/48/64 scale
BORDER RADIUS: 6px (cards), 20px (pills/badges), 4px (input)
SHADOW: Subtle glow effects, tidak heavy drop shadow

KOMPONEN VISUAL:
- Card: Background #1e293b, border-left 3px colored accent, rounded-md
- Badge/Chip: Rounded-full, light background + colored text + colored border
- Button primary: Sky blue gradient, hover glow effect
- Button danger: Rose gradient
- Table: Striped rows, hover highlight, sticky header
- Input: Dark background #0f172a, border slate-700, focus ring sky
- Modal: Centered, backdrop blur, scale-in animation
- Toast notification: Slide-in dari kanan atas

════════════════════════════════════════════
LAYOUT GLOBAL
════════════════════════════════════════════

SIDEBAR (kiri, collapsible):
- Lebar: 260px expanded, 72px collapsed
- Logo Foodinesia di atas
- User info: avatar, nama, role badge (superadmin = sky, viewer = emerald)
- Navigation menu items (dengan icon + label):
  1. 🏠 Dashboard (overview)
  2. 📹 Live Monitoring
  3. 📋 Riwayat Insiden
  4. 👤 Manajemen Identitas (superadmin only)
  5. 📸 Bukti Foto / Laporan (superadmin only)
  6. ⚙️ Pengaturan Sistem (superadmin only)
- Active state: left border sky + background highlight
- Bottom: Logout button + collapse toggle
- Smooth expand/collapse animation

TOPBAR / HEADER (atas):
- Breadcrumb: halaman aktif
- Search global (opsional)
- Notification bell dengan badge count (jumlah pelanggaran baru)
- User avatar quick menu

CONTENT AREA:
- Padding: 24px
- Max-width: fluid (mengikuti layar)
- Background: #0f172a

════════════════════════════════════════════
HALAMAN 0: LOGIN
════════════════════════════════════════════

LAYOUT: Centered form, split screen (kiri: illustration/branding, kanan: form)

KIRI (50%):
- Background gradient dark (slate-900 ke slate-800)
- Logo Foodinesia besar
- Tagline: "CCTV Monitoring & SOP Compliance System"
- Subtle animated dots/grid pattern di background
- Ilustrasi/icon CCTV camera + shield

KANAN (50%):
- Card login form di tengah
- Title: "Masuk ke Dashboard"
- Field:
  ├── Username (icon: user)
  ├── Password (icon: lock, toggle show/hide)
  └── Tombol "Masuk" (full-width, sky gradient, hover glow)
- "Lupa password?" link (text-sm, muted)
- Error state: red border + shake animation + error message
- Loading state: spinner di dalam tombol

ROLE-BASED:
- superadmin → akses semua menu
- viewer → hanya Dashboard, Monitoring, Riwayat

