════════════════════════════════════════════
STATE HANDLING (SEMUA HALAMAN)
════════════════════════════════════════════

LOADING STATE:
- Skeleton shimmer (bukan spinner) untuk cards, table rows, charts
- Pulse animation abu-abu

EMPTY STATE:
- Ilustrasi/icon besar + teks
- Contoh: "Belum ada insiden hari ini" + icon clipboard kosong
- CTA button jika applicable

ERROR STATE:
- Red banner di atas content
- Icon warning + pesan error + tombol retry
- "Gagal memuat data. Coba lagi."

REAL-TIME INDICATOR:
- Titik hijau berkedip di sidebar = Socket.IO connected
- Titik merah = disconnected, auto-reconnecting
- Subtle pulse animation saat data baru masuk

TOAST NOTIFICATIONS:
- Slide-in dari kanan atas
- Tipe: success (emerald), error (rose), warning (amber), info (sky)
- Auto-dismiss 5 detik
- Stack max 3

RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS:
- Desktop: ≥1280px (full layout)
- Tablet: 768-1279px (sidebar collapsed, grid 2 kolom)
- Mobile: <768px (hamburger menu, stack layout, 1 kolom)

════════════════════════════════════════════
ANIMASI & MICRO-INTERACTIONS
════════════════════════════════════════════

- Page transition: fade-in 200ms ease-out
- Card hover: translateY(-2px) + shadow increase
- Button click: scale(0.98) + release
- Modal: backdrop fade-in + content scale from 0.95
- Sidebar expand/collapse: width transition 200ms
- Number counter: count-up animation saat pertama load
- Activity feed: new item slide-in dari atas
- Status dot: pulse animation untuk "online" / "running"
- Tab switch: underline slide transition
- Toggle switch: smooth slide + color change

════════════════════════════════════════════
NAVIGASI & USER FLOW
════════════════════════════════════════════

Login → Dashboard Home (default landing)
       ├→ Live Monitoring
       ├→ Riwayat Insiden → Detail Modal
       ├→ Manajemen Identitas → Add Modal → Encode
       ├→ Bukti Foto → Lightbox Modal
       └→ Pengaturan Sistem → Save/Reset

Sidebar: selalu visible (collapsible), highlight halaman aktif
Breadcrumb: di topbar, menunjukkan posisi current page
Notification bell: klik → dropdown list pelanggaran baru → klik item → ke detail

════════════════════════════════════════════
ROLE PERMISSIONS VISUAL
════════════════════════════════════════════

SUPERADMIN:
- Sees all 6 menu items in sidebar
- Can access Engine Control di Monitoring
- Can CRUD Identities
- Can access Settings
- Can export data

VIEWER:
- Sees only: Dashboard, Monitoring, Riwayat
- NO Engine Control buttons
- NO delete/edit actions
- Read-only view of data
- Menu items hidden (bukan disabled)

Desainkan semua halaman di atas dengan konsistensi visual yang tinggi, 
feel premium/enterprise-grade, dan perhatian detail pada setiap state 
(loading, empty, error, success). Gunakan color palette yang sudah ditentukan. 
Prioritaskan dark mode yang nyaman dilihat dalam durasi lama (untuk supervisor 
yang memantau sepanjang shift).
